4Geeks Academy offers a Full Stack Developer Bootcamp designed to equip students with essential programming skills in JavaScript and Python. Over the course of 18 weeks, attendees will learn to build websites, create applications using front-end libraries, and utilize APIs to enhance functionality. The program features three classes per week, with a low teacher-to-student ratio. No prior coding knowledge is required, and classes are available in both English and Spanish. Graduates will receive a Full-Stack Developer certificate upon completion and gain practical experience through a final project. For more details, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/part-time-full-stack-developer). stop